{"tid":2490822,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"量寬嚴重 今年樓價升15%","createTime":"2021-04-16T01:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:43:07.000Z","uid":166360,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ff667587394801b94e18cbdd73e4b5632b897e4c","tid":2490822,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"量寬嚴重 今年樓價升15%<br />\n09:00 2021/04/16<br />\n<br />\n&quot;差餉物業估價署2月份樓價指數報384.5點，連升2個月，按月上升0.9%，創7個月高位。今年首兩個月，樓價累升1.13%。筆者預期本港樓價會穩步上揚，全年樓價有望上升15%。主要原因是量化寬鬆厲害，息口又低，樓市會是一個良好儲蓄的投資工具......<br />\n<br />\n撰文： 陳永傑 中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2933037/%E9%87%8F%E5%AF%AC%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%20%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%8715%25?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2933037%2F%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%2520%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%258D%258715%2525%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=8f53522b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2933037/%E9%87%8F%E5%AF%AC%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%20%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%8715%25?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">等睇樓淡反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fd9f00c7b6314542845801975b99a68aa54bdce3","tid":2490822,"uid":226886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"@韓林兒 入黎喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50efaba851ddde452b4a505f8c31ebb8070f841a","tid":2490822,"uid":121182,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"錢既購買力下降左, 50年前美孚新邨2萬幾蚊一個單位, 呢家2萬幾蚊一呎...<br />\n起樓同加人工永遠追唔上QE速度, 所以咪買樓保值囉, 好簡單既道理姐<br />\n<br />\n樓淡忘想2021樓價好似沙士咁插法, 係不切實際, 錢就一直係咁印, 業主收到你既錢仲要諗方法快啲洗左佢, 防止貶值, 你話佢點會平賣俾你呀?"},{"pid":"54003